title: Professional.Farmer.2014.Platinum.Edition-TiNYiSO
description:
Professional Farmer 2014: Platinum Edition (c) UIG Entertainment

Release On : 1 july 2014
Disk Amount/Format: 1 DVD ISO
Type of Game : Farming Simulator Media
Protection : Steam
Take up the challenge of professional agriculture and get set for a
dynamic and wide-ranging farm simulation experience. Hook up the plough,
re-fill the tractor or unload the harvest - you control and operate a
wide variety of authentic machinery and equipment. Farm management,
cultivating fields, planting crops, care for animals, buying & selling
produce, and more! Climate and changing seasons influence the game,
providing the player with a constant channel of tasks and activities.
Construct new buildings and acquire more land. Are you ready for the
country life? Heres your opportunity to find out with the most extensive
farming simulation ever!

Features:

Challenging missions that offer hours of engrossing fun in Campaign Mode
or enjoy the game without restrictions in Free Play Mode

Contains the add-ons America and Good Ol Times

Two maps to play on: good old Europe and sunny America

Features authentic tractors and farming machinery from major equipment
manufacturers such as John Deere

The changing seasons and yearly planning play a factor in your success

Learn how to play the game with the Tutorial mode
Burn/mount, install, copy crack, play!
